### versions of button 
btn-outline-secondary 

disabled ----- fades out button either give as class or as parameter. 

data-bs-toggle = 'button' ----- then it has button toggle feature, meaning property changes in toggle manner. 
this is a custom data attribute that allow to hook some properties with JS.

for screen reader we can give some properties like area... 

area-pressed = true , if we button.active as initial value.. 

### button group 
div.btn-group ---> makes groups similar to that of input group. 

or btn-group-vertical --> to stack them vertially.



